headline: 2 Reasons to Like QCOM (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Over the last six months, Qualcomm shares have sunk to $153.85, producing a disappointing 7.7% loss - worse than the S&P 500’s 1.2% drop. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
